<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٥)</span>: م.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو خَيْثَمَةَ:</span> المَكُّوك: المُدُّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>